msgid ""
"This document focuses on the Ascend-specific view: how graph mode works "
"on Ascend, which components are involved, how to configure them, and what"
" constraints users should keep in mind."
msgstr "本文档侧重于 Ascend 特有的视角：图模式在 Ascend 上如何工作、涉及哪些组件、如何配置它们，以及用户应注意哪些约束。"

