#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/graph_mode.md:31
msgid "How Graph Mode Works on Ascend"
msgstr "图模式在 Ascend 上的工作原理"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/graph_mode.md:33
msgid ""
"The default graph path on Ascend involves two stages: **compile-time "
"optimization** and **runtime capture/replay**. ACLGraph handles the "
"runtime capture/replay. The compile-time stage differs by "
"`cudagraph_mode`:"
msgstr "Ascend 上的默认图路径涉及两个阶段：**编译时优化**和**运行时捕获/重放**。ACLGraph 处理运行时捕获/重放。编译时阶段因 `cudagraph_mode` 而异："

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/graph_mode.md:35
msgid ""
"**FULL / FULL_DECODE_ONLY**: Npugraph_ex optimizes the FX graph via "
"torchair (`run_eagerly=True`, compile-time only, no capture). The "
"optimized callable is then captured and replayed by ACLGraph at runtime."
msgstr "**FULL / FULL_DECODE_ONLY**：Npugraph_ex 通过 torchair (`run_eagerly=True`，仅编译时，无捕获) 优化 FX 图。然后，优化后的可调用对象在运行时由 ACLGraph 捕获和重放。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/graph_mode.md:36
msgid ""
"**PIECEWISE**: Npugraph_ex is disabled. Only basic FX fusion passes are "
"applied at compile-time. ACLGraph captures and replays the resulting "
"callable at runtime."
msgstr "**PIECEWISE**：Npugraph_ex 被禁用。编译时仅应用基本的 FX 融合过程。ACLGraph 在运行时捕获并重放生成的可调用对象。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/graph_mode.md:37
msgid "**NONE**: No compilation or graph capture. The model runs in eager mode."
msgstr "**NONE**：无编译或图捕获。模型以即时执行模式运行。"

