msgid "Explicit configuration"
msgstr "显式配置"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/graph_mode.md:129
msgid ""
"To explicitly control Npugraph_ex or enable additional features like "
"static kernel:"
msgstr "要显式控制 Npugraph_ex 或启用静态内核等附加功能："

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/graph_mode.md:155
msgid "To disable Npugraph_ex explicitly:"
msgstr "要显式禁用 Npugraph_ex："

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/graph_mode.md:162
msgid ""
"For more details about Npugraph_ex, see the [torchair "
"guide](https://www.hiascend.com/document/detail/zh/Pytorch/730/modthirdparty/torchairuseguide/torchair_00021.html)."
msgstr "有关 Npugraph_ex 的更多详细信息，请参阅 [torchair 指南](https://www.hiascend.com/document/detail/zh/Pytorch/730/modthirdparty/torchairuseguide/torchair_00021.html)。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/graph_mode.md:164
msgid "Using XliteGraph"
msgstr "使用 XliteGraph"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/graph_mode.md:166
msgid ""
"XliteGraph is an optional path for Llama, Qwen dense series models, Qwen "
"MoE series models, and Qwen3-VL. It requires Xlite to be installed and "
"configured through `xlite_graph_config`."
msgstr ""
"XliteGraph 是 Llama、Qwen 密集系列模型、Qwen MoE 系列模型和 Qwen3-VL 的可选路径。它需要安装 Xlite "
"并通过 `xlite_graph_config` 进行配置。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/graph_mode.md:168
msgid "Install Xlite first:"
msgstr "首先安装 Xlite："

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/graph_mode.md:202
